  <name>ArkRinth</name>
  <summary>A modern Minecraft launcher and mod manager</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      ArkRinth is a modern Minecraft launcher and mod manager based on Modrinth.
      It provides a clean and intuitive interface for managing your Minecraft
      installations, mods, and modpacks.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Modern and intuitive user interface</li>
      <li>Easy mod and modpack management</li>
      <li>Multiple Minecraft version support</li>
      <li>Fast and reliable mod downloads</li>
      <li>Profile management for different setups</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
